ics." O 0[4] "Product Information. One-Alpha (alfacalcidol)." Pharmel Inc, Montreal, IN.[5] "Product Information. Rocaltrol (calcitriol)." Roche Laboratories, Nutley, NJ.[6] "Product Information. Hectorol (doxercalciferol)." Genzyme Corporation, Cambridge, MA.', 1767363022);
